{
    "name": "Cataboligne",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Catabolignes are the devastating siege engines of the qlippoth, rampaging among demonic fortifications and unmaking everything in their path. The treelike growth on a cataboligne\u2019s back is capable of unleashing a beam of entropic power that turns all it touches to dust, while its mouth drools a terrible flesh-eating poison. Oddly, catabolignes do not seem hostile toward proteans, who will often merrily lead these devastating qlippoth on destructive sprees. <br/><br/>A cataboligne is 30 feet tall and 40 feet long, and weighs 16 tons."
        }
    ],
