                "name": "Devastating Strike",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A cataboligne\u2019s slam attacks ignore the first 10 points of hardness of objects and creatures it damages. A creature struck with a critical hit from a cataboligne\u2019s tail slap must succeed at a DC 34 Fortitude save or be stunned for 1 round. The save DC is Strength-based. "
